🎯 Use Cases

Film students analyzing directorial styles
Movie enthusiasts exploring thematic patterns
Data visualization practice and learning
Text analysis educational projects
Cinema research and academic studies

📈 Example Output
The tool generates word clouds that highlight:

Most frequent words in larger font sizes
Common themes across a director's work
Storytelling patterns and preferred vocabulary
Visual representation of narrative elements

🛠️ Technical Details

Language: Python 3.6+

Libraries Used:
pandas: Data manipulation and analysis
numpy: Numerical operations
matplotlib: Data visualization
wordcloud: Word cloud generation


Input: Director name (case-insensitive)
Output: Visual word cloud display
